# What I Practiced

- Created buckets using the AWS Management Console
- Uploaded, downloaded, and deleted objects
- Configured bucket policies for read/write access
- Practiced the same operations using AWS CLI commands:
    - `aws s3 mb s3://my-bucket`
    - `aws s3 cp file.txt s3://my-bucket/`
    - `aws s3 ls s3://my-bucket/`
    - `aws s3 rm s3://my-bucket/file.txt`

